Clang plugins for collecting declaration information from C headers

Depedencies
===========

LLVM/Clang 3.3 (built from source)
CMake 2.8
sqlite3
sqlite3-devel

Build Howto
===========

1. Change LLVM_SRC_DIR, CLANG_SRC_DIR, LLVM_BUILD_DIR and CLANG_BUILD_DIR to
   your local path to LLVM source/build directories.

2. Execute:
    [xx@xx clang-plugins]$ mkdir build
    [xx@xx clang-plugins]$ cd build
    [xx@xx build]$ cmake ..
    [xx@xx build]$ make

Install Howto
=============

1. Execute:
    [xx@xx build]$ cp lib/*.so ../..
